OL,3,CWomen Riders World Relay to lead TT
OL,4,Clegacy lap
OL,6,FThe Isle of Man TT 'Legacy Lap' will
OL,7,Fbe led by the Women Riders World Relay
OL,8,F(WRWR), forming part their mission to
OL,9,Fconnect female riders around the world.
OL,11,FRiders will gather at the grandstand
OL,12,Fon Sunday 31 May, bringing the TT
OL,13,Fcommunity together for a speed-
OL,14,Fcontrolled, open-roads convoy around
OL,15,Fthe 37.73-mile Mountain Course.
OL,17,FThe convoy will be led away by female
OL,18,Friders participating, marking a new
OL,19,Fchapter in the tradition.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
