OL,3,CWomen Riders World Relay to lead TT
OL,4,Clegacy lap
OL,6,FIt was first introduced as a memorial
OL,7,Flap in memory of Simon Andrews, who
OL,8,Fdied in 2014, after a racing incident
OL,9,Fat the North West 200.
OL,11,FSince then, the Legacy Lap has grown
OL,12,Finto a shared celebration of the
OL,13,Fpeople, stories, and machines that
OL,14,Fhave shaped the heritage of the Isle
OL,15,Fof Man TT Races - whether as
OL,16,Fcompetitors, officials, or supporters.
OL,18,FThe first relay organised by WRWR
OL,19,Fconnected 20,000+ women across 102+
OL,20,Fcountries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
