PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776103864
OL,3,CWomen Riders World Relay to lead TT
OL,4,Clegacy lap
OL,6,FWRWR's Isle of Man Ambasaador Lisa,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Women Riders World Relay is
OL,8,Fincredibly proud to lead the 2026 TT
OL,9,FLegacy Lap and to see women riders at
OL,10,Fthe front of such an iconic event.
OL,12,F"The TT has always been about passion,
OL,13,Fcommunity and respect for the Mountain
OL,14,FCourse, and this year's Legacy Lap is
OL,15,Fa chance to celebrate all of those
OL,16,Fthings together.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
