FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776103864
OL,3,CWomen Riders World Relay to lead TT
OL,4,Clegacy lap
OL,6,F"Seeing women at the front of the
OL,7,Fconvoy sends a powerful message that
OL,8,Fmotorcycling is for everyone and
OL,9,Freflects WRWR's mission to connect
OL,10,Fwomen riders around the world, inspire
OL,11,Fthem to be the best they can be, and
OL,12,Fchallenge perceptions of what women
OL,13,Friders can achieve.
OL,15,F"We are honoured to help lead this
OL,16,Fspecial moment on the Isle of Man."
