OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776103864
OL,3,CWomen Riders World Relay to lead TT
OL,4,Clegacy lap
OL,6,FRiders are being asked to gather at
OL,7,F8:30am in the Pit Lane at the TT
OL,8,FGrandstand in Douglas, where a one-
OL,9,Fminute 'Sound of Thunder' will see
OL,10,Ffans rev their engines for one minute
OL,11,Fas a shared tribute before they depart.
OL,13,FThe convoy will then set off at 9:30am
OL,14,Funder the instruction of the Clerk of
OL,15,Fthe Course.
